It's cat dancing videos saying,  

977
01:27:27,680 --> 01:27:32,800
"This is why memory prices have doubled and 
you can't get a new gaming GPU or desktop." 

978
01:27:33,440 --> 01:27:37,360
It's going to be even worse when memory 
prices double again, especially DRAM. 

979
01:27:37,360 --> 01:27:42,000
Another interesting dynamic is that 
it's not just DRAM, it's also NAND. 

980
01:27:42,000 --> 01:27:46,000
NAND is also going up in price.
Both of these markets have expanded capacity very  

981
01:27:46,000 --> 01:27:54,800
