The price increases of DRAM will be larger than  

985
01:28:09,840 --> 01:28:13,440
those of NAND because you've released 
more from the consumer, and in fact,  

986
01:28:13,440 --> 01:28:18,960
you've produced more memory for AI.
Sorry, maybe you just explained  

