So they decided they weren't building new fabs. 

1001
01:29:34,400 --> 01:29:40,000
The market slowly recovered over time but 
never really got amazing until last year. 

1002
01:29:40,560 --> 01:29:44,880
In 2024, we were banging on the drums 
that reasoning means long context,  

1003
01:29:44,880 --> 01:29:48,000
which means a large KV cache, which 
means you need a lot of memory demand. 

1004
01:29:48,560 --> 01:29:50,880
We've been talking about that 
for a year and a half, two years. 

1005
01:29:51,600 --> 01:29:55,760
People who understand AI went 
really long on memory then. 

1006
01:29:57,680 --> 01:30:01,440
So you’ve seen that dynamic, but now 
it has finally played out in pricing. 

1007
01:30:01,440 --> 01:30:05,200
It took so long for what was 
obvious: long context means the KV  

1008
01:30:05,200 --> 01:30:09,440
