large knock-on effects in the economy. 

1018
01:30:56,960 --> 01:31:02,240
So why can't we build more capacity?
There's nowhere to put the tools. 

1019
01:31:02,240 --> 01:31:06,320
It's not just EUV; there are other 
tools involved in DRAM and logic. 

1020
01:31:06,320 --> 01:31:11,840
In logic, for N3, about 28%  

1021
01:31:11,840 --> 01:31:18,960
of the cost of the final wafer is EUV.
When you look at DRAM, it's in the teens. 

1022
01:31:19,520 --> 01:31:22,480
It's going up, but it's a much 
smaller percentage of the cost. 

1023
