That is the hope currently. Everyone's  

1084
01:37:17,440 --> 01:37:24,480
roadmap for 3D DRAM is that you'll still use EUV 
because you want to have that tighter overlay. 

1085
01:37:24,480 --> 01:37:28,720
When you're doing these subsequent processing 
steps, everything is vertically stacked and you  

1086
01:37:28,720 --> 01:37:32,640
