You want the pitches to be tighter. 

1087
01:37:33,440 --> 01:37:35,360
So generally, people are still 
trying to do it with EUV. 

1088
01:37:35,360 --> 01:37:40,480
But what 3D would do is change the calculation 
of how many bits a single EUV pass can make. 

1089
01:37:42,240 --> 01:37:47,360
That number would go up drastically if you 
go to 3D DRAM. That is the hope. Right now,  

1090
01:37:47,360 --> 01:37:56,400
everyone's roadmap goes from the current 6F cell, 
to a 4F cell, and then finally 3D DRAM by the end  

1091
01:37:56,400 --> 01:38:00,080
