likely cross into the 20% range. 

1110
01:39:33,840 --> 01:39:39,760
But then, if we get to 3D DRAM, the total end 
wafer cost as a percentage of EUV tanks again. 

1111
01:39:39,760 --> 01:39:43,760
I guess you care less about the percent of cost 
and more about how much it bottlenecks production. 

1112
01:39:43,760 --> 01:39:50,160
Right, but the percentage of cost—
It’s a proxy, yeah. If you're Jensen  

